509
00:39:50,982 --> 00:39:53,974
<i>[Alex] Dear Nim.</i>
<i>After some serious soul-searching...</i>

510
00:39:54,052 --> 00:39:59,319
<i>I've decided to travel to</i>
<i>20 degrees south, 162 degrees west.</i>

511
