<i>unusual connections.</i>

513
00:40:05,697 --> 00:40:10,964
<i>I cannot say for sure when I'm arriving,</i>
<i>but please know that I am on my way.</i>

514
00:40:11,036 --> 00:40:16,633
<i>If for some reason I never arrive,</i>
<i>it probably means... I'm lost at sea.</i>

515
00:40:16,708 --> 00:40:18,835
<i>Sincerely, Alex Rover.</i>

516
00:40:20,912 --> 00:40:23,574
- Alex Rover is coming?
- [Squawks]

