00:42:24,803 --> 00:42:28,739
Everything!
[Groans]

549
00:42:28,807 --> 00:42:32,038
<i>[Horn honks]</i>

550
00:42:39,984 --> 00:42:43,818
- [Panting]
- You all right there, lady?

