00:43:02,373 --> 00:43:04,534
We're not movin' yet.

557
00:43:04,609 --> 00:43:08,568
Yeah, well, it-it's really the-
It's really the idea of motion that sickens me.

558
00:43:09,247 --> 00:43:10,111
<i>[Tires screeching]</i>

559
00:43:10,682 --> 00:43:12,411
<i>This is what we gotta do, Freddie.</i>

560
00:43:12,484 --> 00:43:15,749
We have to keep 'em in the bay.
Now, Alex Rover's on his way.

561
00:43:15,820 --> 00:43:17,913
<i>We've just gotta hold them</i>
<i>off our beach.</i>

562
00:43:17,989 --> 00:43:21,447
It's pure and simple. Lines of defense,
like the Peloponnesians.

