00:44:56,321 --> 00:44:58,050
Next!

589
00:45:00,458 --> 00:45:04,053
<i>[Pump rattling]</i>

590
00:45:06,931 --> 00:45:09,627
- [Sputtering]
- Oh, no! No! No!

591
00:45:09,701 --> 00:45:11,931
Don't!
